## Module Display

This module Life.Display is responsible for converting the simulation state into a readable visual representation for display in the user interface.

```elixir
defmodule Life.Display do
  @size 30

  def as_table(grid) do
    for y <- 0..(@size - 1) do
      for x <- 0..(@size - 1) do
        if Map.get(grid, {x, y}) == 1, do: "⚫️", else: "⚪️"
      end
    end
  end
end
```

