## Validation / Evaluation of the Solution

This inspection belowconfirms the distributed execution of the simulation by showing that different cells are running on different BEAM nodes, namely the master and the worker.

```elixir
cells = Life.Coordinator.pids()
{node(cells[{0, 10}]), node(cells[{0, 20}])}

```

<!-- livebook:{"output":true} -->

```
{:"master--qpinq7kp@127.0.0.1", :"worker@127.0.0.1"}
```

```elixir
# Afficher l'état d'une cellule spécifique
grid = Life.Coordinator.grid()
cell_15_15 = Map.get(grid, {15, 15})
IO.puts("Cell (15,15) state: #{cell_15_15}")

# Compter les cellules vivantes
alive_count = grid |> Map.values() |> Enum.sum()
IO.puts("Alive cells: #{alive_count}/900")
```

